Tucker McGuire https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tucker_McGuire 0 Tucker McGuire (29 January 1913 in Winchester, Virginia, USA - 3 August 1988 in London, England) was an American-born actress who appeared largely in British films and television. She was born as Anne Tucker McGuire, and married the actor Tom Macaulay.
